- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper discusses the control and energy management system in microgrids, which falls under the scope of systems and control. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper mentions the use of intelligent EMSs in microgrids, which involves artificial intelligence techniques. 
- cs.CY (Computers and Society): The paper touches upon the economics and business models of microgrids, which relates to the societal impact of technology. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering): The paper may involve software engineering aspects in the development of microgrid control and energy management systems. 
- cs.ETM (Emerging Technologies): The paper discusses the potential of microgrids to bring new technologies into the mainstream, which falls under the scope of emerging technologies.
